<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= content_for(:title) || "Toyota Nont Mockup" %></title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="application-name" content="Toyota Nont Mockup">
    <meta name="mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>

    <%= yield :head %>

    <%# Enable PWA manifest for installable apps (make sure to enable in config/routes.rb too!) %>
    <%#= tag.link rel: "manifest", href: pwa_manifest_path(format: :json) %>

    <link rel="icon" href="/icon.png" type="image/png">
    <link rel="icon" href="/icon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/icon.png">

    <%# Includes all stylesheet files in app/assets/stylesheets %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag :app, "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
    <%= javascript_importmap_tags %>
  </head>

  <body class="min-h-screen bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,_rgba(245,158,11,0.14),_transparent_34%),linear-gradient(180deg,_#f6f5f1_0%,_#f2f1ed_100%)] text-stone-900">
    <main class="mx-auto min-h-screen w-full max-w-[1500px] px-4 py-4 lg:px-6 lg:py-6">
      <div class="grid min-h-[calc(100vh-2rem)] gap-4 lg:grid-cols-[260px_minmax(0,1fr)]">
        <aside class="rounded-[2rem] border border-white/70 bg-white/90 p-5 shadow-[0_24px_70px_rgba(28,25,23,0.10)] backdrop-blur">
          <div class="flex h-full flex-col">
            <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-stone-200 bg-stone-50 px-5 py-6">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-amber-700">Toyota</p>
              <h1 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-stone-950">Stock Flow</h1>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-stone-500">Prototype สำหรับฝ่ายจัดสรรและฝ่ายขายในการมองเห็น forecast, รายการสั่ง และ stock กำลังเข้า</p>
            </div>

            <nav class="mt-6 space-y-2">
              <%= link_to root_path, class: sidebar_link_classes(root_path) do %>
                <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-stone-100 text-stone-700"><%= sidebar_icon(:home) %></span>
                <span>Overview</span>
              <% end %>
              <%= link_to forecasts_path, class: sidebar_link_classes(forecasts_path) do %>
                <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-stone-100 text-stone-700"><%= sidebar_icon(:forecast) %></span>
                <span>Forecast</span>
              <% end %>
              <%= link_to stock_orders_path, class: sidebar_link_classes(stock_orders_path) do %>
                <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-stone-100 text-stone-700"><%= sidebar_icon(:orders) %></span>
                <span>รายการสั่งเข้า Stock</span>
              <% end %>
              <%= link_to incoming_stocks_path, class: sidebar_link_classes(incoming_stocks_path) do %>
                <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-stone-100 text-stone-700"><%= sidebar_icon(:incoming) %></span>
                <span>Stock กำลังเข้า</span>
              <% end %>
            </nav>

            <div class="mt-8 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-stone-200 bg-stone-50 px-5 py-4 text-sm text-stone-600">
              <p class="font-medium text-stone-900">Demo Notes</p>
              <p class="mt-2 leading-6">กด `Sync` เพื่อจำลองข้อมูลตอบกลับจากบริษัทแม่ และดูการไหลของรายการจาก forecast ไปเป็น incoming stock</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-auto rounded-[1.5rem] border border-stone-200 bg-white px-5 py-4">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-stone-400">Workspace</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-stone-900">Allocation Team</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-stone-500">ใช้ sidebar นี้เพื่อสลับมุมมองหลักของ flow</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>

        <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-white/70 bg-white/80 p-4 shadow-[0_24px_70px_rgba(28,25,23,0.08)] backdrop-blur lg:p-6">
          <% if notice.present? %>
            <div class="mb-4 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-emerald-800">
              <%= notice %>
            </div>
          <% end %>
          <% if alert.present? %>
            <div class="mb-4 rounded-2xl border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-rose-800">
              <%= alert %>
            </div>
          <% end %>

          <%= yield %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
